title: Chance the Rapper Features on Rapper Kyle’s New Track, ‘Remember Me?’
content: Chance the Rapper hopped onto a new track by Kyle, a simply named California-based rapper who appeared on the Surf track “Wanna Be Cool.” The new song, “Remember Me?,” off of Kyle’s upcoming album Smyle, is a very chill, jazzy number with a slick hook from Chance. Stream it via Fake Shore Drive....
